== 英语中的刚果语外来词 ==
* [[美国英语|美国南部英语]]单词"goober"，意思是[[花生|花生]]，来源于刚果语"nguba"。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bartleby.com/61/16/G0191600.html|title=Bartleby.com: Great Books Online -- Quotes, Poems, Novels, Classics and hundreds more|website=www.bartleby.com|language=en|access-date=2017-07-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328052814/http://www.bartleby.com/61/16/G0191600.html|archivedate=2008-03-28|df=}}</ref>
* 「殭屍」的英文單詞"zombie"來自剛果語的''nzombie''，原意是「死人」，而''Nfumu ya nzombie''是「死人的首領」，用來指稱基督教的上帝。
* [[放克|放克]]（一種源於美國的音樂風格）的英文單詞"funk"，有人認為來自剛果語的''Lu-fuki''。<ref>Farris Thompson, in his work Flash Of The Spirit: African & Afro-American Art & Philosophy</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://english.stackexchange.com/questions/17228/where-does-funk-and-or-funky-come-from-and-why-the-musical-reference|title=Where does "funk" and/or "funky" come from and why the musical reference?|website=english.stackexchange.com|access-date=2017-07-21|archive-date=2017-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011135352/https://english.stackexchange.com/questions/17228/where-does-funk-and-or-funky-come-from-and-why-the-musical-reference|dead-url=no}}</ref>
